soundcrowd F-Droid Repo

This repository contains soundcrowd music player app and extensions.

Currently it serves 7 apps. To add it to your F-Droid client, scan the QR code (click it to enlarge) or use this URL:

https://soundcrowd.github.io/fdroid/repo
